    <note>Li(2) Jizhong [990] Yuanfu coalition. Daxing's [3533], Dayi's [3534], and Dali's [7041] grandfather. Daxing was appointed Junqi shaojian in 1194 and then promoted to Zhedong tiju in the same year. Dayi was appointed Jiangzuo jian zhubu in 1193, promoted to Sinong sicheng in the same year, appointed Kuizhou yunpan in 1194 and dismissed as Jingxi yunpan in 1202. Daxing's and Dayi's brother, Dali [7041], was Meng(2) Song's [1364] son-in-law. Chen Fuliang, WJ, 18.6b; XCB, 504.16b, 16b (n.); Liangchao beiyao, 7.31a; Lou Yue, WJ, 35.24b, 41.21a; SS, 395.3b-4b. CBD, 2, 1057-8.</note>
